{"tid":2332540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指藏士巴拿噴漆等　三青年罪成還押候判　官：勿對量刑抱太多幻想","createTime":"2020-12-19T16:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T07:39:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b3555445e8b4e7c89e1d0a1387eb9c56f7f2f174","tid":2332540,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"網民去年 11 月 11 日發起「三罷」，其中在天水圍天瑞村，凌晨有人堵路及破壞輕鐵站。3 男子在天瑞村遭警員截查，搜出士巴拿及索帶等物，被控管有物品意圖摧毀或損害財產等共4罪，經審訊後昨（18日）在屯門裁判法院被判被裁定所有控罪罪成，須還押至明年 1月 4 日判刑。裁判官水佳麗今日裁定所有涉案證物的證供鏈完整，亦表示作供的警員無令她感覺刻意講大話、不誠實。裁判官裁定三被告管有涉案物品。<br />\n<br />\n在考慮三被告管有涉案物品是否意圖摧毀或損害財產， 或者意圖作非法用途使用時，裁判官指，案發當日凌晨4時，天瑞輕鐵站遭人破壞，從呈堂片段可見，現場有噴漆塗鴉及火燒痕跡。三人分別於凌晨5時多，在距離已破壞了的輕鐵站不遠處遭截查，並搜出鉗、士巴拿、鐵錘、打火機、煮食油的膠樽、酒精、噴漆、頭巾、勞工手套、防毒、面具過濾器等。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官稱，這些物品都是每日在電視上看到，參與社運的人士會攜帶的物品。參與社運的人士不一定是示威者或搞破壞的人，但從 3 被告的被捕時間和地點，加上 3 人無出庭解釋物品的用途，唯一不可抗拒的推論，就是3 人管有涉案物品意圖參與破壞，或提供給他人破壞，因此裁定三人四罪罪成。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至1月4日判刑，先為三被告索取感化官、更生中心、教導所及勞教中心報告。裁判官表明案件有一定程度的嚴重性，感化官報告只用作參考 3 人背景，提醒對量刑「唔好存太多幻想」。3 人需還押候刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E5%A3%AB%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E7%AD%89-%E4%B8%89%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%91-%E5%AE%98-%E5%8B%BF%E5%B0%8D%E9%87%8F%E5%88%91%E6%8A%B1%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%BB%E6%83%B3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%2591-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%258A%25B1%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25B9%25BB%25E6%2583%25B3%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=63ab34c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%2591-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%258A%25B1%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25B9%25BB%25E6%2583%25B3%2F&h=61d60728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E5%A3%AB%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E7%AD%89-%E4%B8%89%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%91-%E5%AE%98-%E5%8B%BF%E5%B0%8D%E9%87%8F%E5%88%91%E6%8A%B1%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%BB%E6%83%B3/</a>"},{"pid":"fbca31c26351d8a578168664709f8a7304be3e55","tid":2332540,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7210ffe85730ac4b8b7bbd399b27c547e630073","tid":2332540,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2fdeeb9c92f658a79d33345790ba8233f2a654","tid":2332540,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"